fields.description_en: Address the underlying causes of decline of migratory species by mainstreaming relevant conservation and sustainable use priorities across government and society
Reduce the direct pressures on migratory species and their habitats
Improve the conservation status of migratory species and the ecological connectivity and resilience of their habitats
Enhance the benefits to all from the favourable conservation status of migratory species
Enhance implementation through participatory planning, knowledge management and capacity building
